727660f-a.title: Queens: Otis Avenue - 108th Street
727660f-a.text:
0tis Ave., north side, between 108th Street and Corona Ave.,
showing Smiths Shady Lake farmhouse. This is the rear view looking
northward.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

727661f-b.title: Queens: Otis Avenue - 108th Street
727661f-b.text:
Otis Ave., north side, between 108th St. (left) and Corona Ave.
Nright, showing in the center of the view, under the spreading fir
tree, the rear and side of the Shady Lake farmhouse which belonged
to J. H. Smith in 1852. See other views located as Corona Ave.,
west side opposite Fifty-fourth Ave. for more data.
1922
Views 2 \& 3:April 1923.
View 4: Feb. 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
MAY BF REPRODUCED.
